data.meta_description: Download this stock image: Belgium's Queen Paola, left, along with her husband King Albert II of Belgium, right, are surrounded by guests at the Royal Castle of Laeken outside Brussels, Sunday Sept. 2, 2007. The Queen invited some 800 persons to celebrate her 70th anniversary. The Queen's birthday is actually on Sept. 11.
